==English==

===Adjective===
{{en-adj}}

# [[Slow]]. When repeated, adagio, adagio, it directs the movement to be very slow.

===Adverb===
{{en-adv}}

# a directive in written music to play [[slowly]], [[leisurely]], and [[gracefully]].

===Noun===
{{en-noun}}

# A piece of music in adagio time; a slow movement; as, an adagio of [[Haydn]].

